{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2107270, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 409484, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "搭配乐器？", "timestamp": 1626844922, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2107368, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 409484, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "以一般流行歌曲为例，作曲作词就是把主唱唱啥写出来，有的会编排一下和弦。而编曲就是选择这个歌段落怎么安排，每个段落用什么乐器伴奏、怎么伴奏", "timestamp": 1626845384, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2107407, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 409484, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "flstudio", "timestamp": 1626845618, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2108195, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 409484, "reply_to": 2107368, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 作曲一般只包括人声旋律吗", "timestamp": 1626851972, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2111648, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 409484, "reply_to": 2108195, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我也不是很专业，但我觉得现代商业唱片音乐里面的作曲（Song writing）应该就只是人声旋律吧，但古典音乐里面的作曲（Compose）肯定不止这些", "timestamp": 1626884840, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2111714, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 409484, "reply_to": 2108195, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 有些流行音乐的作曲还包含配和弦的工作，比如之前看五月天《成名在望》的创作过程里，阿信把和弦都配好了但也只是作词作曲。但肯定也有不配和弦的，比如一大帮连乐理都不懂的歌手，他也不可能配得出来那些和弦", "timestamp": 1626885208, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2111731, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 409484, "reply_to": 2108195, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 总的来说，作曲应该是个灵感>乐理和技术的活儿，很多不懂很多乐理但旋律感很好的人也能完成（比如隐形的翅膀的作曲）。但编曲则是纯纯的技术活", "timestamp": 1626885336, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2113537, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 409484, "reply_to": 2111731, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: wow感谢Bob！！！", "timestamp": 1626926004, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 4, "pid": 409484, "reply": 8, "tag": null, "text": "有没有朋友可以通俗地讲讲编曲是个什么工作？", "timestamp": 1626844772, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1626926001, "url": "", "vote": {}}}